---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { MessageCircle, Target, BookOpen, Users, CheckCircle, ArrowRight } from 'lucide-react';
---

<BaseLayout title="Therapy Articles & Resources | RealMindSolutions" description="Comprehensive therapy resources—guides, platform reviews, therapy types explained, finding the right therapist, and everything you need to know about starting therapy.">
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-b from-white via-brand-primary-50/30 to-white pt-16 pb-12 md:pt-24 md:pb-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12">
      <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-6">Therapy Resources</h1>
      <p class="font-serif italic text-lg md:text-xl text-neutral-600">Everything you need to understand therapy and find the right treatment for you.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-white py-12 md:py-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-12">
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          Whether you're considering therapy for the first time or looking to switch approaches, this resource hub brings together our comprehensive therapy content: platform reviews, therapy type explanations, therapist selection guides, and practical advice for getting the most out of treatment.
        </p>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Essential Therapy Resources</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-12">
        <a href="/resources/guides/therapy-types-explained" class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-200 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <BookOpen className="h-6 w-6 text-purple-600 mb-3" />
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Therapy Types Explained</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-3">CBT, DBT, psychodynamic, EMDR, ACT, and more—understand different therapy approaches.</p>
          <div class="flex items-center text-sm text-brand-primary font-semibold">
            <ArrowRight className="h-4 w-4 mr-1" />Explore Therapy Types
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/guides/selection/finding-the-right-therapist" class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-200 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <Users className="h-6 w-6 text-green-600 mb-3" />
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Finding the Right Therapist</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-3">How to find, vet, and choose a therapist who's the right fit for your needs.</p>
          <div class="flex items-center text-sm text-brand-primary font-semibold">
            <ArrowRight className="h-4 w-4 mr-1" />Read Guide
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/best/platforms" class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-200 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <Target className="h-6 w-6 text-blue-600 mb-3" />
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Best Therapy Platforms</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-3">Compare top online therapy platforms and find the best option for your situation.</p>
          <div class="flex items-center text-sm text-brand-primary font-semibold">
            <ArrowRight className="h-4 w-4 mr-1" />Compare Platforms
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/tools/matchers/therapy-type-finder" class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-200 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <CheckCircle className="h-6 w-6 text-orange-600 mb-3" />
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Therapy Type Finder</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-3">Interactive tool to find the right therapy approach for your needs and goals.</p>
          <div class="flex items-center text-sm text-brand-primary font-semibold">
            <ArrowRight className="h-4 w-4 mr-1" />Find Your Match
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/resources/worksheets/therapy-session-preparation" class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-200 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <MessageCircle className="h-6 w-6 text-pink-600 mb-3" />
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Session Prep Worksheet</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-3">Prepare for therapy sessions and reflect on insights afterward for maximum benefit.</p>
          <div class="flex items-center text-sm text-brand-primary font-semibold">
            <ArrowRight className="h-4 w-4 mr-1" />Download Worksheet
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/resources/guides/insurance-coverage-guide" class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-200 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <CheckCircle className="h-6 w-6 text-indigo-600 mb-3" />
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Insurance Coverage Guide</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-3">Navigate mental health insurance benefits and maximize reimbursement.</p>
          <div class="flex items-center text-sm text-brand-primary font-semibold">
            <ArrowRight className="h-4 w-4 mr-1" />View Guide
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 to-white rounded-lg p-8 mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">What to Expect from Therapy</h2>
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Therapy is a collaborative process where you work with a trained professional to address mental health concerns, develop coping skills, and work toward your goals. Here's what you should know:</p>
          <ul class="text-gray-700 space-y-2">
            <li><strong>Confidential and safe:</strong> What you share in therapy stays private (with rare exceptions for safety)</li>
            <li><strong>Collaborative:</strong> You and your therapist work together as a team toward your goals</li>
            <li><strong>Takes time:</strong> Progress isn't linear, and meaningful change typically takes several weeks or months</li>
            <li><strong>Requires active participation:</strong> The more you engage, the more you'll benefit</li>
            <li><strong>Evidence-based:</strong> Most therapists use approaches proven effective through research</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200 p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Therapy Blog Articles</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">We're building a comprehensive library of therapy-related articles covering topics like:</p>
        <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-sm text-gray-700 mb-6">
          <li>• How to prepare for your first therapy session</li>
          <li>• What to do when therapy isn't working</li>
          <li>• How to talk to your therapist about difficult topics</li>
          <li>• Therapy vs. coaching: understanding the difference</li>
          <li>• How long should you stay in therapy?</li>
          <li>• Breaking up with your therapist: how to end therapy</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Check back soon for new articles, or explore our existing therapy resources above.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-gray-50 py-12 md:py-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Related Topics</h2>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <a href="/blog/tag/therapy-types" class="px-4 py-2 bg-white hover:bg-gray-100 rounded-full text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 transition-colors">Therapy Types</a>
        <a href="/blog/tag/therapists" class="px-4 py-2 bg-white hover:bg-gray-100 rounded-full text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 transition-colors">Therapists</a>
        <a href="/blog/tag/therapist-selection" class="px-4 py-2 bg-white hover:bg-gray-100 rounded-full text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 transition-colors">Therapist Selection</a>
        <a href="/blog/tag/online-therapy" class="px-4 py-2 bg-white hover:bg-gray-100 rounded-full text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 transition-colors">Online Therapy</a>
        <a href="/blog/tag/mental-health" class="px-4 py-2 bg-white hover:bg-gray-100 rounded-full text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 transition-colors">Mental Health</a>
        <a href="/blog/tag/insurance" class="px-4 py-2 bg-white hover:bg-gray-100 rounded-full text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 transition-colors">Insurance</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
